'''Nadim Tabet''' (wavutse 1982), ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri Libani . <ref>https://www.beirutartresidency.com/karine-nadim</ref> Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime izwi cyane ''Imwe muriyi minsi'' . <ref>https://mubi.com/cast/nadim-tabet</ref> <ref>https://elcinema.com/en/person/2128185/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1982 i Beirut, muri Libani. <ref>https://www.ouest-france.fr/culture/entretien-au-liban-un-cinema-ancre-dans-l-histoire-6740843</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Kuva akiri muto, yakundaga gukora firime. Yatangiye gufata amashusho hamwe nibihimbano bibiri bigufi muri videwo, iyambere ''Caravane'' muri 1997 hanyuma ''Kodak colr'' muri 1998. Nyuma yimukiye mu Bufaransa mu 1999 kugira ngo akomeze amasomo ye mu bumenyi bwa muntu na sinema muri kaminuza ya Sorbonne . Hagati aho, ayobora ikabutura ''Histoires extraordinaires du cinématographe'' mu 1999. <ref>[http://www.abboutproductions.com/viewDirectorA?id=21 http://www.abboutproductions.com/viewDirectorA?id=2]</ref> Yakomeje kuyobora ikabutura mu myaka yakurikiyeho, nka ''Martine et Alia'' mu 2001, ''Passé présent futur'' mu 2002, na ''L'Arche de Noé'' mu 2003. Muri 2005, yakoze ''Violante'' ngufi, na ''Le Liban en automne'' muri 2006. Bombi bakiriye neza kandi Tabet yakoze ubutaha bwa''Jeunes et innocents'' muri 2007. Hanyuma muri 2008 yakoze ''Spring 75'' na ''Souvenirs d'un été'' muri 2011. <ref>https://www.onassis.org/people/nadim-tabet</ref> Muri 2014, yakoze ''Eté 91'' ngufi.

Mu 2001, Tabet yashinze iserukiramuco rya sinema ryo muri Libani. <ref>http://meditalents.net/nadim-tabet-2/</ref> Kuva mu 2011, yabaye umwe mu bagize komite ishinzwe gutoranya iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Oberhausen. Amaze gukora filimi ngufi yamamaye cyane, yayoboye filime ye yambere yumukobwa''One of These Days'' muri 2017. nyuma yaje gutsindira igihembo cyiza cyambere cyambere muri Festival ya 22 yabarabu. Muri 2019, yayoboye urukurikirane rwa ''Faraya'' hamwe nundi mukinnyi wa firime wo muri Libani Mounia Akl. <ref>https://www.dohafilminstitute.com/financing/projects/grants/faraya</ref>

